thread.title: Dennis and Dianna Armstrong
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Dennis and Dianna Armstrong

author: Dennis and Dianna Armstrong
title: Dennis and Dianna Armstrong
text:
We found Nelson Alexander to be professional, engaging, open and inclusive, warm and friendly. We had comfort knowing that Nelson Alexander had out property in their best interest and wanted us to get the best possible price for the property. After an unpleasant interaction with another real estate agency, Nelson Alexander welcomed us with open arms and a friendly smile.
With Special Thanks to the lovely team at Nelson Alexander Preston, and specifically our Agents Colin Abbas and Arthur Psarras.
